      <title>苏里南敦促埃克森美孚和道达尔能源公司合并天然气开发</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/ceraweek-suriname-presses-exxon-totalenergies-combine-gas-developments-2024-03-20/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苏里南国有石油公司负责人周二晚间告诉路透社，苏里南国有石油公司Staatsolie已开始与石油巨头埃克森美孚和TotalEnergies进行谈判，鼓励联合开发横跨苏里南和圭亚那海上边界的天然气田。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/ceraweek-suriname-presses-exxon-totalenergies-combine-gas-developments-2024-03-20/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 14:48:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>梅赛德斯-奔驰将在拉施塔特工厂测试 11 MWh 电池以利用电力波动</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/mercedes-benz-test-11-mwh-battery-harness-power-swings-rastatt-plant-2024-03-20/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[梅赛德斯-奔驰周三表示，将从 2025 年起在其位于德国的拉施塔特汽车工厂测试 11 兆瓦时 (MWh) 电池，以帮助缩小可再生能源产量波动与其制造需求之间的差距。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/mercedes-benz-test-11-mwh-battery-harness-power-swings-rastatt-plant-2024-03-20/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 14:47:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
